Barclays Said to Add to Covered Bonds Due 2014, 2022

-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 
2011-12-12T10:37:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-12/barclays-said-to-add-to-covered-bonds-due-2014-2022.html
Barclays Plc (BARC)  is adding to its
covered bonds due in September 2014 and March 2022, according to
a person with knowledge of the deal.  The bank is selling at least 250 million euros of 2014
bonds that may be priced to yield about 105 basis points more
than the benchmark mid-swap rate, the person said. Itâ€™s also
issuing at least 250 million euros of 2022 securities that may
yield about 130 basis points over swaps, the person said.
